 21cm\nsignature from the Intergalactic Medium produced by the Wouthuysen-Field effect\nwill in general trace the peculiar velocity field of the gas in addition to its\ndensity structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Nov 2008 17:23:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
