itself. The jet axis is parallel with the projected direction of motion of NGC\n7626 (inferred from the symmetry axis of the merger cold front), and the\nsouthern leading jet is foreshortened as compared to the northern trailing one,\npossibly due to the additional ram pressure the forward jet encounters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Nov 2008 21:02:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Jan 2009 18:32:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
